{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>PixelPlay Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background-color: #ff6666;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #ff4d4d;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            color: #f0f0f0;\n        }\n        .games-section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #333333;\n        }\n        .games-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #ff6666;\n        }\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #f2f2f2;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin: 20px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 300px;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n        .game-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .game-card h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #ff4d4d;\n        }\n        .game-card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #555555;\n        }\n        .footer {\n            background-color: #cc0000;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .floating-shapes {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n        .shape {\n            position: absolute;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;\n        }\n        .shape1 { top: 10%; left: 20%; width: 80px; height: 80px; animation-duration: 10s; }\n        .shape2 { top: 50%; left: 70%; width: 120px; height: 120px; animation-duration: 9s; }\n        .shape3 { top: 80%; left: 40%; width: 60px; height: 60px; animation-duration: 11s; }\n        .shape4 { top: 30%; left: 90%; width: 90px; height: 90px; animation-duration: 8s; }\n        .shape5 { top: 60%; left: 10%; width: 110px; height: 110px; animation-duration: 12s; }\n\n        @keyframes float {\n            0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); opacity: 0.7; }\n            50% { transform: translateY(-50px) translateX(30px); opacity: 0.3; }\n            100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); opacity: 0.7; }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            h1 { font-size: 3em; }\n            .game-card { width: 80%; margin: 15px auto; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"floating-shapes\">\n            <div class=\"shape shape1\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape shape2\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape shape3\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape shape4\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape shape5\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>PixelPlay Studios</h1>\n            <p>Crafting worlds, one pixel at a time!</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"games-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Games</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ffcccc/ff6666?text=Game+1\" alt=\"Game Cover\">\n                <h3>Galactic Guardians</h3>\n                <p>Embark on an epic space adventure to save the galaxy!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ffcccc/ff6666?text=Game+2\" alt=\"Game Cover\">\n                <h3>Chrono Quest</h3>\n                <p>Travel through time, solve ancient puzzles, and uncover hidden secrets.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ffcccc/ff6666?text=Game+3\" alt=\"Game Cover\">\n                <h3>Munch Mania</h3>\n                <p>A fast-paced arcade game where speed and reflexes are key!</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 PixelPlay Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}